	file for more detail.

REQUIREMENTS
	* aclocal   (1.4.x or above)
	* automake  (1.4.x or above)
	* Gtk+      (2.4.x or above)
	* libcups   (1.1.17 or above)
	* libxml2   (2.6.x or above)
	* libglade2 (2.4.x or above)


LANGUAGES SUPPORTED
	* English and Japanese


INSTALLATION
	$ ./autogen.sh
	$ make
	# make install

